<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>linkr — your profile, one link</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Syne:wght@400;700;800&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/main.css">
</head>
<body>
<%- include('partials/nav') %>
<main>
  <div class="hero">
    <div class="hero-badge"><span class="pulse-dot"></span>100% Free · No credit card</div>
    <h1>Your links.<br><em>One perfect page.</em></h1>
    <p>Create a stunning profile with all your links.<br>Customise everything. Share one URL.</p>
    <div class="hero-cta-row">
      <a href="/register" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Get started free →</a>
      <a href="/login" class="btn btn-ghost btn-lg">Log in</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="features-grid">
    <div class="feature-card"><div class="fi" style="background:rgba(124,111,255,0.12)">⚡</div><h3>Instant Setup</h3><p>Claim your username and go live in 60 seconds.</p></div>
    <div class="feature-card"><div class="fi" style="background:rgba(255,111,156,0.12)">🎨</div><h3>Fully Customizable</h3><p>Change colors, banner, avatar, bio — make it yours.</p></div>
    <div class="feature-card"><div class="fi" style="background:rgba(111,255,200,0.1)">📊</div><h3>Analytics</h3><p>Track profile views and link clicks in real time.</p></div>
    <div class="feature-card"><div class="fi" style="background:rgba(255,200,111,0.1)">🔗</div><h3>Unlimited Links</h3><p>Add as many social links and URLs as you want.</p></div>
  </div>
</main>
<footer class="site-footer"><span>© 2026 linkr</span><span>Built for everyone ✦</span></footer>
</body>
</html>
